comment: /** * Indicates whether the Signed Data or Enveloped Data instance shall be * base 64 encoded. Default value is false. */
code: /** * Indicates whether the Signed Data or Enveloped Data instance shall be * base 64 encoded. Default value is false. */ public void setToBase64(Boolean toBase64) { this.toBase64 = toBase64. }
protected void logErrorAndThrow(final Logger log, String message) throws CryptoCmsException {     log.error(message).     throw new CryptoCmsException(message). }
